reviews.text: I really enjoy this restaurant. The service is good, especially during lunch and the early dinner hour. The staff is friendly and kind, always willing to help you. I love the food and it is good quality. It is clean and well-managed, so you never fell crowded out or forgotten. I definitely recommend this restaurant.
food is pretty good.
Great value for afternoon tea menu ,beef burger and fries only hkd48 , other options on menu ideal for quick snack

Have not been here for awhile. Food is good. Only grip is the table. They use to have square table that seat four but now they change it to a small round table. Can only sit two person. If you have 4 person, they put 2 small Round table together. Felt little bit odd. I guess they are trying to maximize the seating. Probably the psychology is to have you eat and leave because you feel cramped.
The afternoon tea is yummy. We ordered different types of hamburger. And it just cost fifty something.

reviews.text: A clean, well organised mall with more stores than you can imagine. Well maintained and hygienic restrooms as frequently spaced and the proximity to the MTR is a big plus!

Huge variety! It's great for shopping and dining 👍 they also have a cinema, for entertainment, showing a variety of Western and Asian movies. Pop-up stalls and exhibitions are constantly visiting the mall giving shoppers something interesting to do while walking from shop to shop, or just to celebrate the current events (popular movies, holidays, brands etc.)

Nothing special different from other plaza
It’s crowded. Many mainland people surrounded. 
Although it’s so many restaurant, you need to queue for the restaurant was extremely long.
And the price is not reasonable.
Very disappointed. 
Not recommend.
a grand n morden mall with variaties of dinning places, great to visit...

Many restaurants & cafe, you can find any kind of food & style, this should be the biggest shopping mall at Yuen Long area at moment, very convenient and easy to access, just a min. walk linked with West Rail Yuen Long station.

reviews.text: Tea time, 價錢都要成百蚊, 但唔好味... 兩樣都超油, pizza係浸住油咁上枱, 仲要唔太熱 😔 好失望
漏單補回食物時間太耐

環境越嚟越迫貼，枱與枱很近，傾計要共享，餐湯同食物唔夠熱。
服務…沒有以往良好，不要妄想有良好服務，用茶記服務態度比較貼切。如果用價錢去衡量，百幾蚊一個午餐這個質素就真的很一般

I love the food and it is good quality. It is clean and well-managed, so you never fell crowded out or forgotten. I definitely recommend this restaurant.
